==English==

=== Etymology ===
From French ''[[toilette]]''.

=== Noun ===
'''toilet'''

#a ceramic [[bowl]] that can be flushed down with water after disposing of human [[waste]] in it.
#a [[lavatory]] or [[water closet]], [[w.c.]]
#(''British'', ''Aust'') a [[bathroom]], a room containing a ''toilet'' in it.

